      • updateFileType

        byte[] updateFileType(byte data)
               throws STException
        This command allows the user to modify the file type of a selected file to Proprietary File (0x05) or NDEF File (0x04). This command is executed only when the application and the file are selected and access right have previously been set to 0x00
        Parameters:
        data - 0x04 or 0x05
        Returns:
        the R APDU
        Throws:
        STException
